{"kanda":6,"sarga":81,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"विज्ञायतुमनस्तस्यराघवस्यमहात्मनः ।स निवृत्याहवात्तस्मात् प्रविवेशपुरींततः","trans":"Knowing the highsouled Raghava's mind, Indrajith departed from there and entered the city.","words":[{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"महात्मनः","m":"highsouled"},{"d":"तस्यराघवस्य","m":"that Raghava's"},{"d":"मनः","m":"mind"},{"d":"विज्ञाय","m":"victory"},{"d":"तस्मात्","m":"therefore"},{"d":"आहवात्","m":"from there"},{"d":"निवृत्य","m":"departed"},{"d":"ततः","m":"there"},{"d":"पुरीम्","m":"city"},{"d":"प्रविवेश","m":"entered"}]},{"v":2,"dev":"सोऽनुस्मृत्यवधंतेषांराक्षसानांतरस्विनाम् ।क्रोधताम्रेक्षणश्शूरोनिर्जगामाहाद्युति:","trans":"Recollecting those Rakshasas killed, the heroic, mighty and courageous Indrajith's eyes were red in anger.","words":[{"d":"शूरः","m":"hero"},{"d":"सःमहाद्युति:","m":"mighty Rakshasa"},{"d":"तरस्विनाम्","m":"courageous"},{"d":"वधम्","m":"killed"},{"d":"अनुस्मृत्य","m":"recollecting"},{"d":"क्रोधताम्रेक्षणः","m":"eyes turned red in anger"},{"d":"निर्जगाम","m":"went"}]},{"v":3,"dev":"स पश्चिमेवद्वारेणनिर्ययौराक्षसैर्वृतः ।इन्द्रजित्सुमहावीर्यःपौलस्त्योदेवकण्टकः","trans":"Paulastya (one of the nine mind born sons of Brahma, a scion of sage Paulastya), stupendous hero, a tormentor of Devatas, Indrajith, surrounded by Rakshasas came out through the western gate.","words":[{"d":"सुमहावीर्यः","m":"stupendous hero"},{"d":"देवकण्टकः","m":"tormentor of Devatas"},{"d":"पौलस्त्यः","m":"Paulastya"},{"d":"सःइन्द्रजित्","m":"that Indrajith"},{"d":"राक्षसैः","m":"by Rakshasas"},{"d":"वृतः","m":"surrounded"},{"d":"पश्चिमेनद्वारेण","m":"through the western gate"},{"d":"निर्ययौ","m":"came out"}]},{"v":4,"dev":"इन्द्रजित्तुततोदृष्टवाभ्रातरौरामलक्ष्मणौ ।रणायाभ्युद्यतौवीरौमायांप्रादुष्करोत्तदा","trans":"Indrajith, also witnessing the two brothers Rama and Lakshmana prepared for war, exhibited his trickery.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"there"},{"d":"भ्रातरौ","m":"brothers"},{"d":"रामलक्ष्मणौ","m":"Rama and Lakshmana"},{"d":"रणाय","m":"for war"},{"d":"अभ्युद्यतौ","m":"prepared"},{"d":"दृष्ट्या","m":"witnessing"},{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"मायाम्","m":"by conjuring"}]},{"v":5,"dev":"इन्द्रजित्तुरथेस्थाप्यसीतांमायामयींतदा ।बलेनमहतावृत्यतस्यावधमरोचयत्","trans":"Indrajith, also through a trick, wanted to make illusory Sita and place her in the chariot surrounded by Rakshasas and thought of killing her.","words":[{"d":"इन्द्रजित् तु","m":"Indrajith also"},{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"मायामयीम्","m":"through a trick"},{"d":"सीताम्","m":"Sita"},{"d":"रथे","m":"chariot"},{"d":"स्थाप्य","m":"placed"},{"d":"महता","m":"great"},{"d":"बलेन","m":"army"},{"d":"आवृत्य","m":"surrounding"},{"d":"तस्याः","m":"her"},{"d":"वथम्","m":"to kill"},{"d":"अरोचयत्","m":"thought"}]},{"v":6,"dev":"मोहनार्थंतुसर्वेषांबुद्धिंकृत्वासुदुर्मतिः ।हन्तुंसीतांव्यवसितोवानराभिमुखोययौ","trans":"Evil minded Indrajith, made up his mind to hoodwink every one who decided to kill Sita and went towards the Vanaras.","words":[{"d":"सुदुर्मतिः","m":"evil minded"},{"d":"सर्वेषाम्","m":"every one"},{"d":"मोहनार्थम्","m":"to hoodwink"},{"d":"बुद्धिम्","m":"in his mind"},{"d":"कृत्वा","m":"did"},{"d":"सीताम्","m":"Sita"},{"d":"हन्तुम्","m":"to kill"},{"d":"व्यवसितः","m":"decided"},{"d":"वानराभिमुखः","m":"towards Vanaras"},{"d":"ययौ","m":"went"}]},{"v":7,"dev":"तम्दृष्टवात्वभिनिर्यान्तंसर्वेतेकाननौकसः ।उत्पेतुरभिसङ्क्रुद्धाश्शिलाहस्तायुयुत्सवः","trans":"All the forest animals perceiving Indrajithadvancing became angry and with rocks in hand faced him with enthusiasm.","words":[{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"},{"d":"ते","m":"of them"},{"d":"काननौकसः","m":"forest animals"},{"d":"अभिनिर्यान्तम्","m":"coming towards"},{"d":"तम्","m":"him"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"observing"},{"d":"अभिसङ्क्रुद्धाः","m":"very angry"},{"d":"शिलाहस्ताः","m":"holding rocks in hand"},{"d":"युयुत्सवः","m":"enthusiastically"},{"d":"उत्पेतुः","m":"faced"}]},{"v":8,"dev":"हनूमान् पुरतस्तेषांजगामकपिकुञ्जरः ।प्रगृह्यसुमहच्छृङ्गंपर्वतस्यदुरासदम्","trans":"Hanuman, the elephant among monkeys, taking hold of a huge mountain peak that was difficult to reach marched forward and went.","words":[{"d":"कपिकुञ्जरः","m":"elephant among monkeys"},{"d":"हनूमान्","m":"Hanuman"},{"d":"पर्वतस्य","m":"mountain"},{"d":"सुदुरासदम्","m":"difficult to reach"},{"d":"सुमहत्","m":"huge"},{"d":"शृङ्गम्","m":"peak"},{"d":"प्रगृह्य","m":"taking hold"},{"d":"तेषाम्","m":"marched"},{"d":"जगाम","m":"went"}]},{"v":9,"dev":"स ददर्शहतानन्दांसीतामिन्द्रजितोरथे ।एकवेणीधरांदीनामुपवासकृशाननाम् परिक्लिष्टैकवसनाममृजांराघवप्रियाम् ।रजोमलाभ्यामालिप्तैस्सर्वगात्रैर्वरस्त्रियम्","trans":"Hanuman beheld in the chariot of Indrajith, cheerless Sita with one braid, with no desire to live, emaciated by fasting, wearing a single cloth, body not anointed, covered with dust and dirt all over the body, who was dear to Raghava.","words":[{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"इन्द्रजितः","m":"Indrajith"},{"d":"रथे","m":"chariot"},{"d":"हतानन्दाम्","m":"cheerless"},{"d":"एकवेणीधराम्","m":"with one braid"},{"d":"दीनाम्","m":"piteous"},{"d":"उपवासकृशाननाम्","m":"emaciated with fasting"},{"d":"परिक्लिष्टैकवसनाम्","m":"wearing only one cloth"},{"d":"अमृजाम्","m":"with no desire to live"},{"d":"रजोमलाभ्याम्","m":"covered with dust and mud"},{"d":"आलिप्तै:","m":"without any anointment"},{"d":"सर्वगात्रैः","m":"all over body"},{"d":"वरस्त्रियम्","m":"dear"},{"d":"राघवप्रियाम्","m":"wife of Raghava"},{"d":"सीताम्","m":"Sita"},{"d":"ददर्श","m":"saw"}]},{"v":10,"dev":"स ददर्शहतानन्दांसीतामिन्द्रजितोरथे ।एकवेणीधरांदीनामुपवासकृशाननाम् परिक्लिष्टैकवसनाममृजांराघवप्रियाम् ।रजोमलाभ्यामालिप्तैस्सर्वगात्रैर्वरस्त्रियम्","trans":"Hanuman beheld in the chariot of Indrajith, cheerless Sita with one braid, with no desire to live, emaciated by fasting, wearing a single cloth, body not anointed, covered with dust and dirt all over the body, who was dear to Raghava.","words":[{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"इन्द्रजितः","m":"Indrajith"},{"d":"रथे","m":"chariot"},{"d":"हतानन्दाम्","m":"cheerless"},{"d":"एकवेणीधराम्","m":"with one braid"},{"d":"दीनाम्","m":"piteous"},{"d":"उपवासकृशाननाम्","m":"emaciated with fasting"},{"d":"परिक्लिष्टैकवसनाम्","m":"wearing only one cloth"},{"d":"अमृजाम्","m":"with no desire to live"},{"d":"रजोमलाभ्याम्","m":"covered with dust and mud"},{"d":"आलिप्तै:","m":"without any anointment"},{"d":"सर्वगात्रैः","m":"all over body"},{"d":"वरस्त्रियम्","m":"dear"},{"d":"राघवप्रियाम्","m":"wife of Raghava"},{"d":"सीताम्","m":"Sita"},{"d":"ददर्श","m":"saw"}]},{"v":11,"dev":"तांनिरीक्ष्यमुहूर्तंतुमैथिलीत्यध्यवस्यतु ।बभूवाचिरदृष्टाहितेनसाजनकात्मजा","trans":"He looked at her for a moment and recognised her as Janaka's daughter since he had seen her not long before.","words":[{"d":"मुहूर्तम्","m":"for a moment"},{"d":"ताम्","m":"her"},{"d":"निरीक्ष्य","m":"looked at"},{"d":"मैथिलीति","m":"Mythili"},{"d":"अध्ववस्यतु","m":"recognise"},{"d":"तेन","m":"therefore"},{"d":"सा","m":"she"},{"d":"जनकात्मजा","m":"Janaka's daughter"}]},{"v":12,"dev":"अब्रवीत्तांतुशोकार्तांनिरानन्दांतपस्विनीम् ।दृष्टवारथोस्थितांदृष्ट्वाराक्षसेन्द्रसुतश्रिताम् कंसमर्थितमस्येतिचिन्तयन्समहाकपिः ।सहतैर्वानरश्रेष्ठैरभ्यधावतरावणिम्","trans":"Great Vanara, Hanuman, gazing at miserable, joyless, ascetic woman seated in the chariot, worried, why she is in the chariot. He spoke to the best of Vanara leaders and rushed towards the son of Ravana with them.","words":[{"d":"सःमहाकपिः","m":"that great Vanara"},{"d":"शोकार्ताम्","m":"miserable"},{"d":"निरानन्दाम्","m":"joyless"},{"d":"तपस्विनीम्","m":"ascetic woman"},{"d":"राक्षसेन्द्रसुतश्रिताम्","m":"under the sway of the son of the king of Rakshasas"},{"d":"ताम्","m":"her"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"gazing"},{"d":"अस्य","m":"her"},{"d":"किम्","m":"why"},{"d":"समर्थितम्","m":"seated"},{"d":"इति","m":"thus"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke"},{"d":"चिन्तयन्","m":"worried"},{"d":"तैः","m":"with those"},{"d":"वानरश्रेष्ठैःसह","m":"best of Vanaras रावणिम् son of Ravana"},{"d":"अभ्यधावत","m":"rushed"}]},{"v":13,"dev":"अब्रवीत्तांतुशोकार्तांनिरानन्दांतपस्विनीम् ।दृष्टवारथोस्थितांदृष्ट्वाराक्षसेन्द्रसुतश्रिताम् कंसमर्थितमस्येतिचिन्तयन्समहाकपिः ।सहतैर्वानरश्रेष्ठैरभ्यधावतरावणिम्","trans":"Great Vanara, Hanuman, gazing at miserable, joyless, ascetic woman seated in the chariot, worried, why she is in the chariot. He spoke to the best of Vanara leaders and rushed towards the son of Ravana with them.","words":[{"d":"सःमहाकपिः","m":"that great Vanara"},{"d":"शोकार्ताम्","m":"miserable"},{"d":"निरानन्दाम्","m":"joyless"},{"d":"तपस्विनीम्","m":"ascetic woman"},{"d":"राक्षसेन्द्रसुतश्रिताम्","m":"under the sway of the son of the king of Rakshasas"},{"d":"ताम्","m":"her"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"gazing"},{"d":"अस्य","m":"her"},{"d":"किम्","m":"why"},{"d":"समर्थितम्","m":"seated"},{"d":"इति","m":"thus"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke"},{"d":"चिन्तयन्","m":"worried"},{"d":"तैः","m":"with those"},{"d":"वानरश्रेष्ठैःसह","m":"best of Vanaras रावणिम् son of Ravana"},{"d":"अभ्यधावत","m":"rushed"}]},{"v":14,"dev":"तद्वानरबलंदृष्टवारावणिःक्रोधमूर्छितः ।कृत्वाविकोशंनिस्त्रिंशंमूर्ध्निसीतामकर्षयत्","trans":"Indrajith saw the Vanara army coming towards him, deluded with anger, unsheathed the sword and touched Sita's forehead.","words":[{"d":"रावणिः","m":"Indrajith"},{"d":"तत्","m":"there"},{"d":"वानरबलम्","m":"Vanara army"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"क्रोधमूर्छितः","m":"deluded with anger"},{"d":"निस्त्रिंशम्","m":"unsheathed"},{"d":"विकोशम्","m":"sword"},{"d":"कृत्वा","m":"did"},{"d":"सीताम्","m":"Sita"},{"d":"मूर्ध्नि","m":"forehead"},{"d":"अकर्षयत्","m":"touched"}]},{"v":15,"dev":"तांस्त्रियंपश्यतांतेषांताडयामासरावणि: ।क्रोशन्तींरामरामेतिमाययायोजितांरथे","trans":"As they were looking at Sita on the chariot trickishly constructed, and she was crying saying, 'O Rama, O Rama', he stood and hit her.","words":[{"d":"रावणि:","m":"Indrajith"},{"d":"तेषाम्","m":"of them"},{"d":"पश्यताम्","m":"as they were looking"},{"d":"मायया","m":"trickishly"},{"d":"रथे","m":"on the chariot"},{"d":"योजिताम्","m":"constructed"},{"d":"क्रोशन्तीम्","m":"crying"},{"d":"तांस्त्रियम्","m":"stood"}]},{"v":16,