le"},{"d":"पापपराक्रम","m":"of sinful prowess"},{"d":"निर्घृण","m":"not merciful"},{"d":"यस्य","m":"such"},{"d":"ते","m":"by you"},{"d":"मतिः","m":"mind"},{"d":"त्वाम्","m":"your"},{"d":"दिक्","m":"direction"},{"d":"अनार्यस्य","m":"not noble"},{"d":"ते","m":"to you"},{"d":"कर्म","m":"action"},{"d":"ईदृशम्","m":"this manner"},{"d":"नास्ति","m":"not there"}]},{"v":20,"dev":"च्युतागृहाच्चराज्याच्चरामहस्ताच्चमैथिली किंतवैषापराद्धाहियदेनांहन्तुमिच्छसि ।","trans":"\"This Mythili is sent away from home, from the kingdom, and also distanced from Rama's protection. You are unkind and hitting in this way. What harm has she done?\"","words":[{"d":"मैथिली","m":"Mythili"},{"d":"गृहाच्च","m":"from home"},{"d":"राज्याच्च","m":"from kingdom"},{"d":"रामहस्ताच्च","m":"from Rama's protection"},{"d":"च्युता","m":"distanced"},{"d":"निर्दय","m":"unkind"},{"d":"एनाम्","m":"this way"},{"d":"हन्तुम् यत्","m":"hitting"},{"d":"एषा","m":"like this"},{"d":"तव","m":"you"},{"d":"किम्","m":"what"}]},{"v":21,"dev":"सीतांहत्वातु न चिरंजीविष्यसिकथञ्चन वधार्हकर्मणानेनममहस्तगतोह्यसि ।","trans":"\"Indeed, you will not live long after killing Sita. You deserve to be killed for your actions, that is why you have come into my hands.\"","words":[{"d":"सीताम्","m":"Sita"},{"d":"हत्वा","m":"after killing"},{"d":"कथञ्चन","m":"indeed"},{"d":"चिरम्","m":"long time"},{"d":"न जीविष्यसि","m":"will not live"},{"d":"अनेन","m":"many"},{"d":"कर्मणा","m":"actions"},{"d":"मम","m":"my"},{"d":"हस्तगतः","m":"into my hand s"}]},{"v":22,"dev":"येच स्त्रीघातिनांलोकालोकवध्यैषुकुसतिताः इहजीवितमुत्सृज्यप्रेत्यतान्प्रतिपत्स्यसे ।","trans":"\"You deserve to be killed by the world here. Giving up your life, you will be thrown out and descend to the world with those who killed women have gone, after your death.\"","words":[{"d":"लोकवध्येषु","m":"worthy to be killed by the world"},{"d":"इह","m":"here"},{"d":"जीवितम्","m":"life"},{"d":"उत्सृज्य","m":"giving up"},{"d":"एषु","m":"with them"},{"d":"स्त्रीघातिनाम्","m":"one who kills woman